WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.520 --> 00:00:01.719
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.719 --> 00:00:03.529
How are you all doing today?

00:00:03.834 --> 00:00:05.990
I have some things on my heart.

00:00:06.306 --> 00:00:14.279
I found this prophetic word from Kent Christmas and a dream from Dana Coverstone.

00:00:14.279 --> 00:00:21.900
The Lord has really put Pastor Dana Coverstone on my heart—specifically some of the things He has shown him in these dreams.

00:00:23.749 --> 00:00:32.520
I've been going back through some of the past dreams from basically three or four years ago.

00:00:35.942 --> 00:00:44.934
I really believe he heard the Lord on many of those; some can be prayed away, and some can't.

00:00:45.369 --> 00:00:57.280
The videos I'm going to show you are very important because they go alongside what the Lord showed me about the plague that's coming and the economic collapse.

00:01:04.179 --> 00:01:10.060
Before this year is out, the death angel is being loosed upon the Earth.

00:01:10.520 --> 00:01:23.680
What they concocted and created in laboratories called Coronavirus will pale in comparison, saith the Lord, to the spirit that the death angel will loose upon the nations.

00:01:24.170 --> 00:01:26.870
It will not touch My people.

00:01:26.870 --> 00:01:37.764
For the first virus, the enemy brought it against the innocent and the old, but this, saith God, will not touch the church.

00:01:37.764 --> 00:01:49.240
Some will fall on your right hand, as I declared in Psalm 91, and they will fall on your left hand, but it shall not come nigh unto thy dwelling.

00:01:49.525 --> 00:01:55.710
What you just saw was him saying a thousand shall fall at your side and ten thousand at your right hand.

00:01:55.710 --> 00:02:51.760
If you remember what I said, it goes alongside what the Lord showed me about a glow of honey around the believers.

00:02:51.760 --> 00:03:15.544
We would go in and lay hands on people in cots.

00:03:15.544 --> 00:03:46.070
I saw cots full of bodies and people dying of this virus; it was very tragic.

00:03:46.070 --> 00:04:29.914
I've told everyone about what the Lord showed me, so I won't go over it all again.

00:04:29.914 --> 00:05:21.629
I'm just showing you that there are prophetic voices hearing that another plague and pestilence are coming.

00:05:29.490 --> 00:05:49.140
The Lord was also talking to me about getting in shape.

00:05:49.140 --> 00:06:20.658
I've been lifting weights, trying to bulk up and take care of my body more.

00:06:20.658 --> 00:07:08.120
It's been a challenge balancing eating with working out, but I'm learning a lot on YouTube.

00:07:08.120 --> 00:07:46.875
My family were not people who worked out, so this is all new.

00:07:46.875 --> 00:08:03.940
This is Bonnie Jones, Bob Jones's widow.

00:08:04.647 --> 00:08:43.285
I believe she hears the Lord, and she got a prophetic visitation about a week ago.

00:08:59.470 --> 00:09:25.262
This is a fresh video where the Lord gave her a very stern prophetic warning.

00:09:25.262 --> 00:09:42.720
She heard, 'Beware the dragon,' followed by 'biological warfare.

00:09:42.720 --> 00:10:02.006
' She associated the dragon with China.

00:10:02.006 --> 00:10:54.999
Biological warfare is the deliberate use of disease-causing agents like bacteria or toxins to kill or incapacitate as an act of war.

00:10:54.999 --> 00:11:25.280
I believe China is cooking up another virus that will be more deadly.

00:11:25.280 --> 00:11:46.587
Remember when I told you I saw the dragon?

00:11:46.587 --> 00:12:30.449
In my World War II video, I said the dragon was hiding behind a black rock, waiting for a new season.

00:12:42.466 --> 00:12:45.310
The dragon represented the COVID.

00:12:46.075 --> 00:13:43.800
I was shown in the spirit that they were taking a biological agent in a lab to release on the people, starting in Europe.

00:13:53.679 --> 00:14:12.445
I warned about that in a video called 'The Dream That I Had.

00:14:12.445 --> 00:14:54.494
' Back in April, the Lord told me He was sending another plague and that cataclysmic things would happen.

00:14:54.494 --> 00:15:14.639
He said a line of demarcation has been drawn.

00:15:14.639 --> 00:15:38.599
Calamity is coming because of disobedience to His word.

00:15:38.599 --> 00:16:04.600
Famine is imminent—not just of food, but of the Word.

00:16:04.600 --> 00:16:37.088
There has been a chokehold in America, and now He is going to release it.

00:16:44.849 --> 00:17:42.977
I'm not 100% sure what He means by a famine of food, but catastrophes like earthquakes, floods, and fires will affect our food chain.

00:17:42.977 --> 00:18:35.394
In a vision, I saw John Deere tractors sitting idle with no crops planted from the West Coast to the East Coast.

00:18:35.394 --> 00:18:53.756
There was an extreme drought.

00:18:55.333 --> 00:19:14.987
The Lord said three times, 'There's no water.

00:19:14.987 --> 00:19:54.465
' I saw the Lubbock area, Texas, and through Mexico where it was extremely dry.

00:19:54.465 --> 00:20:10.085
We need to be wise, not fearful.

00:20:10.085 --> 00:20:38.040
We cannot stop judgment, but we can lessen it through prayer.

00:20:38.040 --> 00:21:20.339
Jesus told me face-to-face that this major shaking will take place for a humbling and an awakening.

00:21:20.339 --> 00:21:52.240
We will be a sheep nation because of the prayers of our founding fathers.

00:21:52.240 --> 00:22:21.755
I've seen bridges and earthquakes preventing trucks from crossing, and I've seen gas shortages.

00:22:21.755 --> 00:22:40.534
Pastor Dana also had a dream about an 'Economic Desert.

00:22:40.534 --> 00:23:05.655
' He was at the bottom of an ocean, 2,000 feet below sea level.

00:23:05.655 --> 00:23:22.133
He saw a billboard that said 'Economic Desert.

00:23:22.133 --> 00:23:41.064
' He saw life acting normal, then suddenly changing.

00:23:41.064 --> 00:24:11.635
Cars were parked, trash was everywhere, and people were carrying brown paper grocery bags.

00:24:11.635 --> 00:24:29.994
Eventually, they had no bags, and ATMs were empty.

00:24:29.994 --> 00:25:06.880
At a checkout line, the scanner wasn't working, and a man with an empty wallet began to cry.

00:25:06.880 --> 00:25:47.320
I'm encouraging you to build the kingdom of God and ask Him what you need to do.

00:25:47.320 --> 00:26:01.706
Have some cash and resources set aside.

00:26:01.706 --> 00:26:36.404
It doesn't have to be a lot, but we are headed for hard times.

00:26:44.360 --> 00:26:57.034
I believe in miracles, but Christians will face hard things.

00:26:57.034 --> 00:27:11.240
It's not an easy-peasy life.

00:27:11.240 --> 00:27:39.274
Dana also had a dream about Wall Street and bartering.

00:27:39.274 --> 00:27:54.836
He saw people trading chickens and tools.

00:27:54.836 --> 00:28:22.399
One man traded shotgun shells for chickens; a lady traded hammers for screws.

00:28:22.399 --> 00:28:38.544
Someone traded a Rolex for horses.

00:28:38.544 --> 00:29:00.919
There were no vehicles, only bikes and skateboards.

00:29:00.919 --> 00:29:50.130
In the dream, tables were bowing under the weight of goods like unwashed eggs and rusty hand tools.

00:29:56.311 --> 00:30:15.546
I saw wooden awls and hand drills, but no power tools.

00:30:17.619 --> 00:30:48.330
The man with the shotgun shells was barefoot and used his shirt as a bag.

00:30:59.751 --> 00:31:26.120
A man representing Jesus was there and said, 'You are not as prepared as you need to be.

00:31:26.120 --> 00:31:37.653
Hearken to My word.

00:31:37.653 --> 00:32:07.039
Embrace, don't barter with My word, as you will come up short.

00:32:07.039 --> 00:32:25.618
' This situation might last longer than you think.

00:32:26.244 --> 00:32:40.733
I saw four oak trees representing four years.

00:32:40.733 --> 00:33:22.371
People were not ready for the first year, and by the end, they were bartering for ammo.

00:33:22.371 --> 00:34:15.240
If you live in a major city, think about what it would be like if you didn't have bread for your children.

00:34:15.240 --> 00:34:37.159
Pastor Dana is an elderly man, probably in his late 50s.

00:34:38.736 --> 00:34:56.565
I feel an urgency to warn you.

00:34:56.565 --> 00:35:41.937
I've seen great darkness over 2025, but also a financial outpouring for the body of Christ to provide.

00:35:41.937 --> 00:36:00.102
Mega-churches may close and move to home churches.

00:36:00.102 --> 00:36:17.640
Ask the Lord what you need for your house.

00:36:17.640 --> 00:36:37.075
Maybe it's Ramen noodles or a week's worth of food.

00:36:37.075 --> 00:36:57.900
Even FEMA says to have three days of water.

00:36:59.265 --> 00:37:15.583
Don't operate out of fear, but be alert.

00:37:15.583 --> 00:37:42.540
Every time I look for the prayers of the saints to change the direction.

00:37:42.540 --> 00:38:12.160
In 2015, the Lord gave more time, but this time He says it will manifest.

00:38:18.715 --> 00:38:20.959
I hope this video brings your attention to these things.

00:38:20.959 --> 00:38:55.106
It's smart to have candles and a source of heat for the winter.

00:38:57.173 --> 00:39:05.341
Jesus is coming back.

00:39:05.341 --> 00:39:22.680
Father, I thank You for everyone here.

00:39:22.680 --> 00:39:57.074
You always provided for me, even if it was just a piece of bologna.

00:39:57.074 --> 00:40:14.605
We command fear to bow its knee.

00:40:25.507 --> 00:40:39.149
You are El Elyon, the Most High, and Jehovah Jireh.

00:40:39.149 --> 00:41:01.870
We believe for a hundredfold return and supernatural multiplication.

00:41:13.675 --> 00:41:24.134
We speak to the seeds and the harvest.

00:41:42.999 --> 00:41:44.359
We believe for acceleration, signs, and wonders.

00:41:44.359 --> 00:41:54.667
Peace be with you.

00:41:54.667 --> 00:41:56.280
Shalom.
